<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="id5228a6f1-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Historical and Revision Notes</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Based on title 28, U.S.C., 1940 ed., § 148 (<ref href="/us/act/1911-03-03/ch231/s75">Mar. 3, 1911, ch. 231, § 75</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/36/1108">36 Stat. 1108</ref>).</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Minor changes in phraseology were made.</p>
</note>
